description: Returns a list of the actions taken in a  TestGridSession.

parameters.name: sessionArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the session to retrieve.

nested_items.name: actions
nested_items.description: The action taken by the session.

nested_items.name: action
nested_items.description: The action taken by the session.

nested_items.name: started
nested_items.description: The time that the session invoked the action.

nested_items.name: duration
nested_items.description: The time, in milliseconds, that the action took to complete in the browser.

nested_items.name: statusCode
nested_items.description: HTTP status code returned to the browser when the action was taken.

nested_items.name: requestMethod
nested_items.description: HTTP method that the browser used to make the request.
